dc_description_s: Shows wagon and sled roads, pack trails, railroads, and telegraph and telephone lines.; Relief shown by contours and spot heights.; Insets: [St. Lawrence, Nunivak Island, and Pribilof Islands] --[Aleutian Islands].; Sheets dissected and mounted on one sheet of cloth.|173 x 146 centimeters, sheets 82 x 94 centimeters. or smaller|Scale 1:1,250,000|General Map Collection
